android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION.description: Access fine location sources, such as the Global Positioning System on the phone, where available. Malicious applications can use this to determine where you are and may consume additional battery power.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.RECORD_AUDIO.description: Allows application to access the audio record path.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.MODIFY_AUDIO_SETTINGS.description: Allows application to modify global audio settings, such as volume and routing.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: This flag allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup=true]

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.kawkaw.pornblocker.safebrowser.up.MainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.

nx.description: The shared object has NX bit set. This marks a memory page non-executable making attacker injected shellcode non-executable.

stack_canary.description: This shared object does not have a stack canary value added to the stack. Stack canaries are used to detect and prevent exploits from overwriting return address. Use the option -fstack-protector-all to enable stack canaries.

relocation_readonly.description: This shared object does not have RELRO enabled. The entire GOT (.got and .got.plt both) are writable. Without this compiler flag, buffer overflows on a global variable can overwrite GOT entries. Use the option -z,relro,-z,now to enable full RELRO and only -z,relro to enable partial RELRO.

rpath.description: The shared object does not have run-time search path or RPATH set.

runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

playstore_details.title: Porn Blocker : Safe Search & Web Filter
playstore_details.description:
Porn blocker is a safe browser that safely protects your browsing by blocking millions of porn web sites and explicit adult content, No more porno, while browsing!

Studies show watching too much pornography rewires the brain, can affect your relationships and your mental health, there's certainly enough to suggest that porn has a negative impact on our lives Porn blocker is here to help those who watch porn everyday and are addicted to it to quit Porn Addiction quickly, our app filters porn content and pornographic material from millions of sites on the internet to keep you and your kids safe from images and videos with objectionable content. 
Browse the web with confidence and let your loved ones browse worry free while our porn blocker protects them. 
Garant you automatic family friendly safe-search results for text, images, and videos. Not only safe results in Google but in YouTube as well, you don't have to worry about your kids watching inappropriate videos on YouTube again either.


► AdBlock
	• Blocks annoying ads, pop-ups, banners to help you save mobile data, while giving you a comfortable browsing experience.

► Adult content Blocking
	• Whether you're trying to block porn content for yourself as a porn addict or your child, porn blocker browser blocks millions of porn websites and not allowing Porn videos downloads:

	• Pornography
	• Adult/Mature Content
	• Nudity

► Protect your eyes
	• A Dark theme ( Night mode browser) to enable it anytime in a weak light environment available in the browser's settings.

► Search engine
	• Multiple Safe search engines (Google, Bing, Yahoo, StartPage, DuckDuckGo, etc.) we highly recommend Google Safe search (The default one).

► Ghost Mode
	• Incognito "Ghost Mode": Auto-clean your browsing activities (cookies, sessions and trackers).

► Proxy Browser
	• Browser using Orbot Proxy (turn on TOR proxy support to mask your identify and location), I2P proxy or you can setup you custom proxy manually.

► Fast browser & Fast downloader
	• A lightweight experience by using the WebKit rendering engine that comes built into your Android devices.

► Perfect for families
	• Let your loved ones browse the web with confidence. Install the Porn Blocker on all of your Android device and let the blocker protect them.

► Simple UI with easy and faster browser.
► Incognito Browsing
► Multilingual support
► Fast Download
► Permissions explained
	• permission.INTERNET: Needed to access the internet for browsing
	• permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE: Needed for downloading files and backing up data
	• permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE: Needed for downloading files and restoring data
	• permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION: Needed for sites that want your location (you can deny location access)


If you find inappropriate (adult) content, that is not blocked, please drop us a line. We will fix it as quickly as possible.
